final_desc: - - Lain-lain :Preparat kecantikan atau rias dan preparat untuk perawatan kulit (selain obat-obatan), termasuk preparat penutup atau pelindung kulit terhadap sinar matahari; preparat manikur atau pedikur.;- - Other :Beauty or make-up preparations and preparations for the care of the skin (other than medicaments), including sunscreen or sun tan preparations; manicure or pedicure preparations.
